Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZedasR性能試驗 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過部分改裝也只有這種程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來您不太滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哪台機體讓我滿意過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有耐心等待新機體完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為提高響應速度 正在最後調試階段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這台機體 新型高達也不足為俱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加緊完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經擬定了以我為主抗擊高達的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我 從沒有懼怕過…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「維甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是移民計劃失敗的受害者們…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遺棄在火星圈的人們…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.73,0:02:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立起的新興國家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫在嚴酷環境下生活的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為奪回那座名為「地球」的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策劃起了規模宏大的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達孜 XRounder們的冰眠結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今天吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 據報剛才已經全部甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾哥哥 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見 德西爾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛伏任務歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞您的冰眠結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特此趕來報告哥哥一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 潛伏任務一定夠嗆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣高水平的XRounder
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小享有高度自由的權限 活躍在前線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會像你這樣被派去雜用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而還會受到保護
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特看人從不走眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特司令官 可以進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官 各部隊作戰準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被任命為地球佔領軍司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時哥哥在冰眠中…故未能及時報告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官 你爬到我的頭上去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計抵達作戰宇域前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體將會調試完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要和我說預計
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次作戰意義重大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷進化的機動戰士 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,構成其中樞的AGE系統 就是我們的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據情報 AGE系統的核心部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就置於高達胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰場上隨時收集需要的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說 這次的目標是AGE系統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪取也好 破壞也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎樣 難免與高達一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 竟然有這樣的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方的技術水準完全出乎我們預料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦至今未能解密AGE系統的內部程序
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以至於無法拷貝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要控制它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以阻止高達進一步進化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是高達母艦的預測航線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們中途埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 如果去往聯邦總司令部BIG RING
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最短的路徑…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XD37 巖礁宇域…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號 即將駛入XD37巖礁宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員進入多障礙區域航行態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼那麼沒骨氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想 索敵系統的性能發揮會受到限制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能不被維甘發現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是變更航線的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下要盡可能避免戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥…能避開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗 在想什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是在擔心那傢伙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不！ 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 新兵蛋子 吃得慣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是嚼完了嚥下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓它變成打仗時的力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和正常吃有什麼區別？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼區別 有什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照做就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吃的時候使勁吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別等餓了後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 敵人什麼時候來都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調試已經全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會讓我滿意嗎 Zeydra
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zeydra是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為發揮XRounder實力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專門研發的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊時請記得戴上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是控制傑哈特大人XRounder能力的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更準確的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它有助於能力的穩定發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和機體實現溝通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就傑哈特大人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果最大限度發揮能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體本身會支撐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有力量的不便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短時間內反覆佩卸無法發揮其性能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長期征戰時請平日就戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 紅得就像個靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看 司令官大人的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在說服不了自己和你戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你愁眉苦臉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼話跟我說吧 不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次出戰的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有想過敵人機師的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？沒那種閒工夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有工夫也不會去想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏可是戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人屁股就是被用來打的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們家的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敵系統有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 戰鬥配置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員戰鬥配置 全員戰鬥配置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始對照索敵數據
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各應急班站點就位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會在這條路徑上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋伏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 保養完了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是老爸 是爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 要叫我中尉 說了多少遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 保養完沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…沒問題 亞瑟姆的AGE2也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克中尉GJ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘮嘮叨叨又要被媽媽說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去快回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克先生是你爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都說我像媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敵系統對照完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dorado 6機 Baqto 2機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在這種地方進入戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 新兵蛋子們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巖礁宇域的戰鬥 對你們來說還太早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 敵人來了就沒有不迎接的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為上次的事畏畏縮縮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕就該有點衝勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 沃爾夫隊出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆·明日野 高達AGE2 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫隊 出擊完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對維甘機動戰士部隊 採取迎擊態勢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B543反應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機後方又出現疑似維甘機體1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在以三倍速度接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 你是我的對手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機後方B543 出現疑似維甘機體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向沃爾夫隊接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他機體的三倍速度？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼來頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巖礁宇域裏這種速度？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 保佑我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的們 客人不是只有一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先試試手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也行 就像上次那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一架架來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮靜 鎮靜 鎮靜 鎮靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明機種 闖入機動戰士隊戰鬥宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 我來會會你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是我一廂情願
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 先打下一架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 它奔你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台機體能跟上我的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度嗎 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是新型機的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃得也挺快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧布萊特 麥克斯 阿莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜兵交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是雜兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉莎 我們倆一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 一對一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的對手是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一台在攻擊高達
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他根本不做理睬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看破了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特！ 是傑哈特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 是傑哈特嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 你怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是對手又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫我是又如何 為什麼這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想戰鬥的話 就從戰場上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連撤退的覺悟也沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來此的目的就是擊落高達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你當作朋友 是我的一廂情願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊 傑哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是 這麼好欺負的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度就敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我面前撒野嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來就來 給你個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有衝勁是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了什麼都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 XRounder的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以不適合戰鬥 不只是因為天真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我面前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說 司令官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓高達給逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹩腳的謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放水饒了朋友一命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想騙過我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果伊澤爾坎特大人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己關在房間裏 看來該教訓下他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人 有時候會需要一個人靜下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.59,0:22:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特 是故意放過我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.47,0:22:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想說 我沒有上戰場的實力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XRounder…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:23:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活在父親的陰影下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友搖身一變成為仇敵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆向心中的幻影發起挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.89,0:24:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影之敵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.77,0:24:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zeydra是為最高級別XRounder
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.59,0:24:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特·葛雷德專門製造的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.69,0:24:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XRounder專用機中也性能超群
